gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Suns 129, Jazz 115
gameRecap.excerpt: Kevin Durant (31 points, eight rebounds, seven assists) and Bradley Beal (30 points, seven assists) combine for 61 points as the Suns defeat the Jazz, 129-115. Grayson Allen notched eight points and a career-high 14 assists for the Suns in the victory, while Lauri Markkanen tallied 22 points and five rebounds for the Jazz in the losing effort. The Suns win their third straight game as they improve to 31-21 on the season, while the Jazz fall to 26-27.
